  <Docs>
    <summary>A simple view for displaying a single image.</summary>
    <remarks>If a <see cref="T:GameStack.Graphics.SlicedSprite" /> is provided, the sprite is automtically resized to fit the view frame. Since this operation mutates the sprite's geometry, consider calling <see cref="M:GameStack.Graphics.SlicedSprite.Clone()" /> to create a copy first. Sliced sprites are resized regardless of the <see cref="P:GameStack.Gui.ImageView.Fill" /> setting.</remarks>
